01:48:30,726 --> 01:48:32,758
She's quite the worst maid I've ever had!

1259
01:48:32,958 --> 01:48:35,881
So, why do you keep her?
- I don't know, she reminds me of me.

1260
01:48:37,730 --> 01:48:40,530
Do you have a title?
