01:48:54,353 --> 01:48:55,353
Oh, I'm not going to that.

1266
01:48:55,710 --> 01:48:56,580
Why not?

1267
01:48:57,150 --> 01:48:59,740
Hollywood premieres are not for old trout like me.

1268
01:49:00,926 --> 01:49:02,830
 Anyway, it's not convenient.

1269
01:49:04,740 --> 01:49:06,040
He hasn't invited you, has he?

1270
01:49:10,210 --> 01:49:12,310
Mary Poppins wouldn't stand for that!

1271
01:49:19,452 --> 01:49:22,084
Can I help you?
- I'm perfectly capable, thank you.

1272
01:49:22,284 --> 01:49:23,234
As i recall.

1273
01:49:25,735 --> 01:49:28,455
Sweet of you.

1274
01:49:31,425 --> 01:49:33,924
Walt?
- Hello Dolly!

1275
01:49:33,925 --> 01:49:36,040
Walt?
- Tommie,

1276
01:49:36,530 --> 01:49:39,029
 you're gonna have to move that meeting with G.E.

1277
01:49:41,100 --> 01:49:43,315
What?

1278
01:49:49,370 --> 01:49:51,850
Mrs. Travers!
- Me again!

1279
01:49:52,470 --> 01:49:53,740
How wonderful to see you.

1280
01:49:54,790 --> 01:49:56,030
I'm here for my premiere.

1281
01:49:57,920 --> 01:49:59,390
Great!

1282
01:49:59,880 --> 01:50:02,345
I didn't receive my invitation,
but I just assumed

1283
01:50:02,545 --> 01:50:05,965
 the American postal service had
fallen down on the job, as per usual.

1284
01:50:06,890 --> 01:50:09,790
I'll have a replacement, 
sent to your hotel right away.

1285
01:50:10,200 --> 01:50:14,349
You are very kind, Mr Disney.
I knew you wouldn't have forgotten me.

1286
01:50:15,670 --> 01:50:20,733
Pam, how could I forget you?

1287
01:50:20,933 --> 01:50:27,090
Good evening.

1288
01:50:27,860 --> 01:50:29,270
Hello, could you please order me a cab?

1289
01:50:29,470 --> 01:50:31,479
Absolutely.

1290
01:50:49,470 --> 01:50:50,519
Ralph!

1291
01:50:50,719 --> 01:50:54,763
I had a feeling, a certain friend of mine
might be needing me tonight.

1292
01:51:02,500 --> 01:51:03,550
Wow!

1293
01:51:03,960 --> 01:51:05,040
You look like a million bucks!

1294
01:51:06,030 --> 01:51:07,020
Thank you.

1295
01:51:08,945 --> 01:51:11,906
Let's get you to that ball, huh?
- Thank you, Ralph, thank you.

1296
01:51:59,820 --> 01:52:01,325
This is your night.

1297
01:52:01,525 --> 01:52:05,647
None of this would be possible
without you.

1298
01:54:30,670 --> 01:54:33,570
Sometimes, the person we love.
Through no fault of his own,

1299
01:54:34,470 --> 01:54:35,930
can't see past the end of his nose.

