<i>Ohhh! Let's go fly a kite.</i>

1320
01:56:28,070 --> 01:56:31,452
<i>Up to the highest height.</i>

1321
01:56:31,652 --> 01:56:38,142
<i>Let's go fly a kite and send it soaring,</i>

1322
01:56:38,342 --> 01:56:41,541
<i>Up through the atmosphere..</i>

1323
01:56:41,741 --> 01:56:45,009
<i>Up where the air is clear...</i>

1324
01:57:12,160 --> 01:57:14,211
Don't leave me.

1325
01:57:16,593 --> 01:57:18,361
Never.

1326
01:57:18,561 --> 01:57:22,969
 I promise.
I will never lose you.

